WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.050
People were wondering about

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.670
prayer cues and things like that. They

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:05.990
want to know some more things, so I'm

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.130
going to give you a couple right here.

00:00:07.140 --> 00:00:09.950
Okay, in Ephesians it talks about how we

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.690
wrestle not against flesh and blood, but

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:14.450
against principalities and powers, and

00:00:14.460 --> 00:00:16.010
there's a lot more to the verse. But for

00:00:16.020 --> 00:00:18.529
time's sake, there you go. It's Ephesians

00:00:18.529 --> 00:00:18.539
4:16,

00:00:18.539 --> 00:00:22.090
I believe, somewhere around there.

00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:26.390
You cannot pray against somebody's will.

00:00:26.400 --> 00:00:29.630
Okay, like say you go to work and

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:32.150
your boss is really mean to you. Maybe

00:00:32.160 --> 00:00:35.030
you're a teenager right now and you're

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:38.090
watching me, and you are in a verbally abusive

00:00:38.100 --> 00:00:40.250
relationship with your parents.

00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:42.830
When you are being assaulted like that,

00:00:42.840 --> 00:00:46.910
it is a demonic presence behind it, and

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:51.290
so you take authority over the devil.

00:00:51.300 --> 00:00:53.569
This is how I would do it. I had a boss

00:00:53.579 --> 00:00:56.029
that was not very nice to me, and he

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:59.330
treated me pretty poorly. So every day I

00:00:59.340 --> 00:01:02.569
would drive to work and say, 'I bind the

00:01:02.579 --> 00:01:05.870
maneuvering of any demonic spirits in

00:01:05.870 --> 00:01:05.880
so-and-so,

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:10.250
and you will not torment me in

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:13.730
any way today at all. I take authority

00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:16.190
over the spirits that maneuver inside of

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:20.410
him, and I command them to stop right now.

00:01:20.420 --> 00:01:23.870
You have no right, no power, no authority,

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:26.630
and I bind you up, and you are not able

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.390
to maneuver and torment in any way in the

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:31.450
name of

00:01:31.450 --> 00:01:31.460
Jesus.'Concerning

00:01:31.460 --> 00:01:34.789
abuse, I bind the devils that

00:01:34.799 --> 00:01:37.490
are tormenting my husband or my wife.

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:41.270
I bind that devil in the name of Jesus. I

00:01:41.280 --> 00:01:43.490
command you to cease and desist in your

00:01:43.500 --> 00:01:46.310
maneuvering, and I command you to stop it

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:49.670
right now. You will not

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:53.210
maneuver in them anymore. I command you

00:01:53.220 --> 00:01:54.649
to stop this,

00:01:54.659 --> 00:01:58.969
and I call peace to the spouse, or

00:01:58.979 --> 00:02:01.429
whoever, in the name of Jesus. I call

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:04.910
peace over them, and that's how I pray. I

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:07.670
don't bind them. You can't bind them

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.609
because they have free will, okay? And you

00:02:10.619 --> 00:02:11.930
get into some kind of witchcraft

00:02:11.940 --> 00:02:13.430
sometimes when you start doing that,

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:15.830
praying over their emotions. It's like

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.330
when I'm trying to

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:18.770
sell something in my business or

00:02:18.780 --> 00:02:21.710
whatever. I don't pray over that person,

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:24.229
'Father, I thank you that you cause them

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:29.030
to buy my product.'Okay? I say

00:02:29.040 --> 00:02:32.510
this: 'Father, I thank you that my product

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:36.170
stands out. Father, I thank you that my

00:02:36.180 --> 00:02:39.410
product is desirable, that people want

00:02:39.420 --> 00:02:42.229
what I'm selling. I thank you, Father, that

00:02:42.239 --> 00:02:44.210
I am blessed in the city and the field,

00:02:44.220 --> 00:02:46.130
coming in and going out, according to

00:02:46.140 --> 00:02:49.610
Deuteronomy 28. And Father, I thank you

00:02:49.620 --> 00:02:52.070
that when people see my

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:54.830
stuff and what I'm selling today,

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:57.410
they want what I have because it stands

00:02:57.410 --> 00:02:57.420
out.'But

00:02:57.420 --> 00:02:59.930
I don't pray over their

00:02:59.940 --> 00:03:03.410
emotions manipulating them. You

00:03:03.420 --> 00:03:04.970
don't manipulate people in the

00:03:04.980 --> 00:03:06.650
spirit realm. It's part of

00:03:06.660 --> 00:03:09.050
witchcraft, okay? You don't do that. You

00:03:09.060 --> 00:03:10.850
just pray over your stuff. You pray,

00:03:10.860 --> 00:03:12.649
'Father, my stuff is going to stand out.

00:03:12.659 --> 00:03:15.170
Thank you, Lord.'And Father, when it comes

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:18.410
to your unsaved loved ones,

00:03:18.420 --> 00:03:20.809
if they're out drinking or partying or

00:03:20.819 --> 00:03:22.790
being promiscuous or whatever:

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:26.390
'Father, I thank you for Johnny, or whoever. I

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:28.729
thank you, Father, that he is saved.

00:03:28.739 --> 00:03:30.649
Father, I thank you, Lord, right now that you

00:03:30.649 --> 00:03:30.659
send

00:03:30.659 --> 00:03:32.809
laborers across

00:03:32.809 --> 00:03:32.819
his

00:03:32.819 --> 00:03:35.330
path, whether they're at Walmart or

00:03:35.330 --> 00:03:35.340
wherever.

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:38.570
Let somebody come across his

00:03:38.580 --> 00:03:40.910
path and witness to him today.

00:03:40.920 --> 00:03:43.610
Now, Father, I thank you. I bind the spirit

00:03:43.620 --> 00:03:46.910
of addiction off of his life.

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:50.869
I take authority over alcoholism. I take

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:53.809
authority over drug addiction.'He may be

00:03:53.819 --> 00:03:56.930
strung out on meth or

00:03:56.940 --> 00:04:00.110
prescription pills. 'I bind the spirit of

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:02.270
addiction off of his life right now in

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:05.030
the name of Jesus. I call that spirit to

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:07.729
cease and desist in its maneuvering in

00:04:07.739 --> 00:04:10.910
his life. I command it to bow its knee.

00:04:10.920 --> 00:04:13.970
You have no authority to torment him

00:04:13.980 --> 00:04:16.969
anymore. You're a foul devil, and I

00:04:16.979 --> 00:04:19.729
command you to release him right now in

00:04:19.739 --> 00:04:22.550
the name of Jesus. If they're wayward now,

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:25.610
angels, I send you out. Go and bring

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:28.490
Johnny, or whoever, home to me. Bring them

00:04:28.500 --> 00:04:30.770
home. Father, I thank you, Holy Spirit,

00:04:30.780 --> 00:04:32.990
you're working on their hearts right now.

00:04:33.000 --> 00:04:35.450
I call them to have a heart that's

00:04:35.460 --> 00:04:38.629
pliable. Oh God, I minister to them right

00:04:38.629 --> 00:04:38.639
now.'There

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:40.610
it goes, it started hitting me

00:04:40.620 --> 00:04:41.930
in the intercession.

00:04:41.940 --> 00:04:46.070
Hallelujah.

00:04:46.080 --> 00:04:48.770
'Okay,

00:04:48.780 --> 00:04:50.749
I pray over their heart right now in the

00:04:50.759 --> 00:04:52.490
name of Jesus.

00:04:52.500 --> 00:04:54.530
Call him in,

00:04:54.540 --> 00:04:56.390
bring them in. Lord,

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.490
I thank you. Lord, we're not giving up on

00:04:58.500 --> 00:04:59.330
them.

00:04:59.340 --> 00:05:01.129
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you're

00:05:01.139 --> 00:05:03.770
sending them angels right now. Minister

00:05:03.780 --> 00:05:05.510
to my children.

00:05:05.520 --> 00:05:07.490
Father, I thank you, Lord, that if they're

00:05:07.500 --> 00:05:09.350
in the bar right now, I thank you, Lord,

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:11.150
that there is a conviction over their

00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:13.550
heart to get out of that bar right now in

00:05:13.560 --> 00:05:15.170
the name of Jesus.

00:05:15.180 --> 00:05:17.210
Father, I thank you, Lord, that

00:05:17.220 --> 00:05:19.790
you're going to save their soul. Lord, I

00:05:19.800 --> 00:05:21.409
thank you, Lord, you bring forth the

00:05:21.419 --> 00:05:24.170
harvest right now over my son. Father,

00:05:24.170 --> 00:05:24.180
that

00:05:24.180 --> 00:05:25.850
you would visit him in the

00:05:25.860 --> 00:05:27.890
midnight hour in a dream.

00:05:27.900 --> 00:05:30.050
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you would

00:05:30.060 --> 00:05:32.330
send an angel to minister to him.

00:05:32.340 --> 00:05:34.550
Father, I thank you, Lord, it may be an

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:36.050
angel that they don't even know, an angel

00:05:36.060 --> 00:05:38.510
unaware. It could be a hitchhiker, I don't

00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:40.610
know whoever, that finally walks up to him

00:05:40.620 --> 00:05:43.070
and says boom, and the power of God moves

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:45.350
on him in a supernatural way.'We don't

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:48.950
know, but I know this: that God is able to

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:52.129
do exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:05:52.139 --> 00:05:54.350
we dare ask or think, according to the

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:56.450
power that works in you.

00:05:56.460 --> 00:05:58.249
Okay,

00:05:58.259 --> 00:06:01.490
He's already done it all, folks. He's

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:03.529
already done it all. He's already done

00:06:03.539 --> 00:06:05.330
everything He can do for your healing.

00:06:05.340 --> 00:06:07.430
You've got to stay in agreement with

00:06:07.440 --> 00:06:09.350
what He's already done in His Word.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:12.590
First Peter 2:24, 'By His stripes we are

00:06:12.590 --> 00:06:12.600
healed.'He

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:14.930
was wounded for our

00:06:14.940 --> 00:06:17.450
transgressions, He was bruised for our

00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:20.029
iniquities, the chastisement of our peace

00:06:20.039 --> 00:06:24.590
was upon Him, and with His stripes we are

00:06:24.600 --> 00:06:27.710
healed, period. And we stand on that. We

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:30.050
get in the Word, and we quote the Word

00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:32.689
out of our mouth: 'Father, I thank you, Lord,

00:06:32.699 --> 00:06:35.570
that you provide all my needs according

00:06:35.580 --> 00:06:37.730
to your riches in glory

00:06:37.730 --> 00:06:37.740
in

00:06:37.740 --> 00:06:40.850
Christ Jesus. I thank you, Lord, that I'm

00:06:40.860 --> 00:06:43.610
a tither, I'm a giver, I'm a sower, I'm a

00:06:43.620 --> 00:06:45.830
believer. And Father, you said you would

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:47.930
take care of me. You said you would never

00:06:47.940 --> 00:06:50.390
see the righteous forsaken, nor his seed

00:06:50.400 --> 00:06:52.490
begging bread. And Father, if you take

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:55.129
care of the birds of the air and

00:06:55.139 --> 00:06:59.090
the lilies, how much more am I to

00:06:59.100 --> 00:07:02.330
you? How much more, God? And Father, I thank

00:07:02.340 --> 00:07:04.370
you, Lord, that you're going to take care

00:07:04.380 --> 00:07:07.670
of my family, my children, my wife. You're

00:07:07.680 --> 00:07:10.129
going to provide for us today. I thank

00:07:10.139 --> 00:07:11.990
you, Lord, that you give me a creative

00:07:12.000 --> 00:07:15.710
idea to get wealth. I seek you, Father. I

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:18.650
seek your provision for my house.

00:07:18.660 --> 00:07:21.409
I seek you, God, because you said you take

00:07:21.419 --> 00:07:23.990
care of us. Father, I'm a giver. I thank

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:25.370
you, Lord, that you're going to provide

00:07:25.380 --> 00:07:28.249
for us. I thank you, Lord, that the seeds

00:07:28.259 --> 00:07:29.870
that I've sown are going to bring forth

00:07:29.880 --> 00:07:33.290
some thirty, some sixty, and a hundredfold.'I've always

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:34.550
asked that:

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:38.749
why some thirty, some sixty, and some a

00:07:38.749 --> 00:07:38.759
hundred?

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:41.390
How do I get a hundredfold every time, Lord,

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:43.790
whenever I sacrificially give? And the Lord

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:45.409
said, 'It's the ground you're sowing in,

00:07:45.419 --> 00:07:46.969
son.

00:07:46.979 --> 00:07:49.430
Some ground is miracle-working ground,

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:51.710
and some ground is not as rich as others.

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:55.189
So you've got to be a good student

00:07:55.189 --> 00:07:55.199
of

00:07:55.199 --> 00:07:57.469
where I tell you to give your

00:07:57.469 --> 00:07:57.479
money.'And

00:07:57.479 --> 00:08:00.710
I ask Him, I said, 'Lord, show me

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:02.990
where the hundredfold ground is. Show me

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:05.689
where the 60-fold ground is. Not that I'm not

00:08:05.699 --> 00:08:08.210
grateful for the thirtyfold, but Lord, I know

00:08:08.220 --> 00:08:10.189
that you're exceedingly abundantly above

00:08:10.199 --> 00:08:12.589
all that I dare ask or think. And so,

00:08:12.599 --> 00:08:14.330
Father, I thank you, Lord, that you teach

00:08:14.340 --> 00:08:17.089
me how to sow into the good ground.'And I

00:08:17.099 --> 00:08:19.869
found a lot of times,

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:23.029
blessing Israel ministries, ministries trying

00:08:23.039 --> 00:08:25.670
to get the Jewish people saved,

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:27.650
ministries trying to get the little

00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:32.870
orphans saved—protecting the orphans, the widows'ministries, things

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:33.949
like

00:08:33.949 --> 00:08:33.959
that—they're

00:08:33.959 --> 00:08:36.469
real good soil. Because that's

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:38.630
what Jesus commissioned us to do: to take care

00:08:38.640 --> 00:08:40.490
of the orphan and the widow. Jesus

00:08:43.020 --> 00:08:45.050
told us that those who bless

00:08:45.060 --> 00:08:47.269
Israel, I will bless, and those that curse

00:08:47.279 --> 00:08:49.550
Israel, I will curse. So I'm going to be

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:51.829
on the side of the blessing. I want to be

00:08:51.839 --> 00:08:53.509
on the side that says, 'Lord, I bless

00:08:53.509 --> 00:08:53.519
Israel.'Even

00:08:53.519 --> 00:08:56.210
if I don't always agree with

00:08:56.220 --> 00:08:57.949
what they do and how they live

00:08:57.959 --> 00:08:59.150
their life, because there

00:08:59.150 --> 00:08:59.160
is

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:00.889
a lot of sin with a lot of

00:09:00.899 --> 00:09:02.690
Jewish people. But Father, I'm going to

00:09:02.700 --> 00:09:05.449
honor them. I honor them, and I pray for

00:09:05.449 --> 00:09:05.459
them.

00:09:05.459 --> 00:09:07.130
We don't

00:09:07.140 --> 00:09:08.210
talk bad about them. We just pray, 'Thank

00:09:08.220 --> 00:09:10.430
you, Lord, that you protect Netanyahu,

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:12.410
and you protect the parliament and the

00:09:12.420 --> 00:09:13.790
people that are over that area. And

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:15.590
Father, I thank you, Lord, that they're

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:17.150
going to have a saving knowledge of

00:09:17.150 --> 00:09:17.160
Jesus.'I

00:09:17.160 --> 00:09:19.490
just pray over that kind of

00:09:19.500 --> 00:09:21.949
stuff. That's the way you should be. Speak

00:09:21.959 --> 00:09:24.889
blessing, speak increase.

00:09:24.899 --> 00:09:28.009
Your mountain needs to hear your voice

00:09:28.019 --> 00:09:30.829
in your life. If you're not

00:09:30.839 --> 00:09:32.750
calling those things that be not as

00:09:32.760 --> 00:09:35.269
though they were, you need to be speaking

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:37.430
to your circumstances.

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:41.990
You have what you say. Your tongue is

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:44.509
powerful. If you're speaking cursing out

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:46.130
of your mouth, and speaking doubt and

00:09:46.130 --> 00:09:46.140
unbelief—'Oh

00:09:46.140 --> 00:09:48.889
well, I'm sick today again.

00:09:48.899 --> 00:09:52.850
I've got a bad day. Oh yeah, well, my boss

00:09:52.860 --> 00:09:55.550
is treating me like trash again.

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:58.790
Oh, my kids are acting up again, boy, he is a

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:01.190
real devil'—you're going to get what you

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.769
say. You

00:10:03.769 --> 00:10:03.779
are

00:10:03.779 --> 00:10:05.329
decreeing those things out of

00:10:05.339 --> 00:10:06.430
your mouth.

00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:08.150
Manifestation is going to start

00:10:08.160 --> 00:10:11.570
happening, because life and death are in

00:10:11.580 --> 00:10:16.610
the power of the tongue. Remember that.

00:10:16.620 --> 00:10:19.070
You want to know if you're in

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:21.410
the faith for what you're

00:10:21.420 --> 00:10:22.670
believing for?

00:10:22.680 --> 00:10:25.190
Joy and peace are going to be following

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:25.910
you.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:28.009
You need to be walking in joy and peace.

00:10:28.019 --> 00:10:29.870
If you're in worry, doubt, and unbelief,

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:31.490
you're not

00:10:31.500 --> 00:10:34.670
in faith. If

00:10:34.680 --> 00:10:37.970
you're in a spirit of worry and

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:41.150
you're in fear, fear is not faith. Faith cometh

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:43.009
by hearing, and hearing by the Word of

00:10:43.019 --> 00:10:45.350
God. You've got to get in the Word, and

00:10:45.360 --> 00:10:47.329
you've got to get the Word concerning

00:10:47.339 --> 00:10:49.190
your circumstances. You've got to find

00:10:49.200 --> 00:10:51.949
scripture concerning your healing,

00:10:51.959 --> 00:10:53.569
concerning what you're believing for,

00:10:53.579 --> 00:10:56.210
because faith cometh by hearing, and

00:10:56.210 --> 00:10:56.220
hearing

00:10:56.220 --> 00:10:57.949
by the Word. You've got to get

00:10:57.959 --> 00:11:00.710
that faith inside of you. Perfect

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:04.130
love casteth out all fear, and fear has

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:06.590
torment, okay? So you've got to get these

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:08.690
words in there. He that feareth is not

00:11:08.700 --> 00:11:10.610
made perfect in love, and you've got to

00:11:10.620 --> 00:11:12.350
know that. I believe it's in

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:15.170
First John somewhere. When I'm

00:11:15.180 --> 00:11:17.389
quoting these scriptures to you, you can

00:11:17.399 --> 00:11:19.550
use your Bible app and

00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:21.650
type them in there to help you. I'm

00:11:21.660 --> 00:11:23.329
sorry, it's hard for me to memorize

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:27.889
the street addresses; I just

00:11:27.889 --> 00:11:27.899
memorize

00:11:27.899 --> 00:11:29.590
the words.

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:36.110
